## How to setup?

We now have about 1,000 acres of land. We want to try to manage this land based on DAO. To be honest, we are not sure that this attempt will be 100% successful. We want to try to use the blockchain method to link different roles to join. Come in, let's govern this land together. If this attempt is successful, we will work with the community to promote this method to the world, allowing more land and more people (organizations) to participate, producing more food and supplying more more people, contribute a little to stop the global food crisis.

